title: High Time | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: High Time | Joel Osteen
description:
You are closer than you realize to seeing your dreams fulfilled. Even when we don't see things changing, God wants us to live with a sense of expectancy for the new things He wants to do in our lives.


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
